# bringup/resource MANIFEST
# Maps resource paths to absolute container destination paths.
# Format: <resource_path>  <container_path>
#   resource_path   relative to bringup/resource/
#   container_path  absolute path inside the Docker image
#   Trailing / on both sides: directory copy (recursive, merge)
#   Trailing / on container side only: file copied into directory

